<div class="section_title">Exhibiting At The Venetian?</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=133 hspace=6 src="/images/general/HPAHT_60.gif" width=60 align=right>Check out our new <A href="/about_ces/multimedia.asp">Sands Expo and Convention Center/The Venetian virtual tour</A>. This virtual tour not only helps exhibitors prepare for the show, but also helps attendees navigate the venue so they can find you once they are on-site. The tour demonstrates how to enter through the Sands to access the high-performance audio &amp; home theater meeting rooms exhibits and The Venetian Tower exhibit suites. In addition to illustrating the seamless transition from the Sands to The Venetian, the tour also includes highlights such as the location of the International Commerce Center (ICC) in the Sands Upper Level Lobby, The Venetian’s Palazzo Ballroom (the new home for the International CES keynote addresses), and information about the Sands/Venetian Express shuttle bus.
<P>Take the <A href="/about_ces/multimedia.asp">virtual tour</A> today to make sure you are ready for the 2007 International CES.</P>
