<div class="section_title">Vehicle Communication and Safety TechZone</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG hspace=5 src="/images/general/ITSAmerica.gif" align=right>The Vehicle Communication and Safety TechZone, located in the LVCC Gold Lot, offers a unique exhibit space for automotive technology including navigation, accident avoidance, connectivity, in-vehicle entertainment and internet and traffic management. But don’t just tell attendees what your equipment can do, show them. 
<P>Showcase live demonstrations of automotive warning systems pertinent to traffic and highway management, in-vehicle travel information as well as crash and incident response systems. Display the latest technology in active safety systems such as collision warnings, lane departure and curve over-speed. </P>
<P>This TechZone welcomes automotive OEMs, ME manufacturers, integrators, navigation developers, location based services and telematics companies. </P>
<P><IMG hspace=5 src="/images/general/techzone_small.gif" align=right>CES TechZone exhibitors receive great opportunities, extra publicity and exclusive CES benefits. </P>
<UL>
<LI>Links to the CESweb.org Press Room </LI>
<LI>Promotion at the Industry Forum press conference and NYC press event to more than 500 media </LI>
<LI>Promotion in the Attendee brochure, Pre-Show Planner and other targeted market promotions </LI>
<LI>Features in 20 attendee newsletters, amounting to over 5 million total impressions </LI>
<LI>Flyers in CES literature kiosks and special TechZone signage throughout all CES venues</LI></UL>
<P><A href="/exhibitors/space/techzones.asp">View a list of the 2007 CES TechZones.</A></P>
<P>For information on participating in any of our exciting TechZones, contact a sales representative today. </P>
</span>
